data.description: Modern updates collide w/comfortable living spaces best describes this 2 story home completely remodeled in last 2 years. Enter to large living room w/original hardwood floors restored to their original beauty, exposed brick & abundant windows providing ample natural light. Dining room is flex space w/multiple uses, currently used as office/den. Kitchen updated w/new white cabinets, high def. laminate counters, subway tile backsplash, vinyl plank flooring & stainless steel appliances. Updates include NEW roof 2023, new HVAC, new vinyl insulated windows, new vinyl siding, new front door, white woodwork & paneled doors.Awesome front porch, completely rebuilt and ready for the porch swing. Bsmt is clean & offers glass block windows. Big yard, mostly fenced. near busline, mins to downtown
